---
title: Honey Beef Koftas & Garlic Yoghurt Hummus with Roast Cauliflower & Carrot Couscous
description: You will be floating on clouds with this beef kofta and couscous dinner. A flavourful honey drizzle coats the koftas and
will send your tastebuds to dreamland, especially when you add a fragrant hummus and yoghurt combo.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
